# 3) Page Frontend #2 : “Bet Recommendations” (prochains matchs)

## Objectif

Proposer une liste de paris **justifiés**, cohérents avec tes modèles et ta gestion du risque.

### Inputs

* League(s)
* Date range (next 7 days)
* Market filter (1N2, HT, corners, cards)
* Risk profile (conservative / balanced / aggressive)
* Stake rule (flat / fractional Kelly)
* Bookmaker + bet time rule

### Sortie : table de recommandations

Colonnes :

* Match / date
* Market / line
* Selection
* Model probability
* Implied probability (normalized)
* Edge
* Odds now
* Expected value (EV)
* Confidence score (stabilité modèle + data quality + lineup known?)
* “Why” (top 3 features drivers / notes)
* “Do not bet if…” (ex: lineup missing, odds moved, low coverage)

### Garde-fous

* Ne jamais proposer si :

  * data coverage insuffisante (no stats / no features)
  * model not champion/active
  * predictions non calibrées (flag)
* Si lineups pas confirmés : tag “PRE-LINEUP” vs “POST-LINEUP”

